REWARD SYSTEM & COLLECTIBLES ASSETS

Place the following PNG files in this directory:
BADGES:
- badge-gold.png (gold badge template)
- badge-silver.png (silver badge template)
- badge-bronze.png (bronze badge template)
- icon-star-badge.png (achievement icon: speed/bonus)
- icon-speed-badge.png (achievement icon: fast solving)
- icon-streak-badge.png (achievement icon: streak milestone)

TREASURES:
- treasure-chest-closed.png (unopened chest icon)
- treasure-chest-open.png (open chest with shine)

MUSEUM:
- math-museum-bg.png (gallery background for collectibles)

These assets support the Reward System & Collectibles feature for the "Math Museum" screen.
Recommended size: 128x128px for badges/icons, 256x256px for chests
